XML-Atom-Filter

XML::Atom::Filter eases creation of command line tools to filter and
process Atom feeds.

This release of XML::Atom::Filter works with Atom 1.0 feeds when used with
XML::Atom 0.13_01 or later.


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    * XML::Atom 0.11


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


